### Check Inventory - Multiple Items
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/default/V1/shops/{{shopId}}/integration/inventory/check
Authorization: Bearer {{sharedSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "sku": "{{productSku}}",
      "quantity": 2,
      "product_id": "{{productId}}"
    },
    {
      "sku": "24-MB01",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

